<refsect1 id="gst-plugins-bad-plugins-gloverlay.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>Overlay GL video texture with a PNG image</para>
<refsect3><title>Examples</title><informalexample><programlisting><![CDATA[
gst-launch-1.0 videotestsrc ! gloverlay location=image.jpg ! glimagesink
]]></programlisting></informalexample>
<para>
FBO (Frame Buffer Object) is required.</para>
</refsect3>

